nodes.bodyText: The pom.xml looks like it's targeting 1.7
nodes.diffHunk:
@@ -0,0 +1,19 @@
+on:
+  pull_request:
+    paths:
+    - 'WCP/fdahpStudyDesigner/**'
+    - '.github/workflows/build-studybuilder.yml'
+name: Build studybuilder
+jobs:
+  build:
+    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
+    steps:
+    - uses: actions/checkout@v2
+    - name: Set up JDK 1.8
+      uses: actions/setup-java@v1
+      with:
+        java-version: 1.8

nodes.bodyText: Modified to 1.7 , however build got failed due to compilation error . As few of the classes used java 8 functionalities . Hence reverted back to java 1.8
